| venmo                     | [Venmo](https://venmo.com/)                         |                                    | `USD`                         | вљЎпёЏ рџ§Є рџ’ё    |
| uplinkapi                 | Uplink API Test asset                               |                                    | `NZD`                         | рџ§Є          |
