### Flags

 * вљЎпёЏ : **Supports Live Assets** -- Add `.main` to the Asset Type e.g. `centrapay.nzd.main`.
 * рџ§Є : **Supports Test Assets** -- Add `.test` to the Asset Type e.g. `centrapay.nzd.test`.
 * рџљ« : **Restricted Asset** -- Cannot be used to pay for "restricted" [Line Items](/api/payment-requests#line-item-model).
 * рџ’ё : **Supports Quick Pay** -- Can be used to quick pay a [Payment Request](/api/payment-requests).
 * рџ’ј : **Requires Tax Number** -- [Tax Number](/api/businesses#tax-number-model) must exist on the Merchant's Business to transact this asset type.
